fields.description: This assignment covers an introduction to algebraic expressions, topics include identification of algebraic expressions and addition of algebraic expressions.

This assignment continues the introduction to algebraic expressions, topics include multiplication of algebraic expressions, standard algebraic identities, algebraic substitution and division of algebraic expressions.
This assignment covers area of 2-dimensional shapes.
This assignment covers surface area of 3-dimensional objects.
This assignment covers volume of 3-dimensional objects.
This assignment covers both volume and surface area of 3-dimensional objects (advanced).
This assignment covers Integer Operations, Number Line concepts and Fractions.
This assignment covers Decimals and Simple Equations.
This assignment covers Ratio and Proportion, the Unitary Method and Percentages.
This assignment covers Rational Numbers, Algebraic Expressions and Exponents.
This assignment covers an introduction to exponents and powers. Topics include laws of exponents, standard-usual form conversion and multiplicative inverse.
This assignment reinforces exponents and powers concepts, covering simplification and evaluation of exponents.
This assignment focuses on Factorisation. The concepts covered are Factors of Natural Numbers, Factors of Algebraic Expressions, Factorisation by Common Factor and Factorisation by Regrouping.
This assignment focuses on Factorisation. The concepts covered are Factorisation using Identities, Factorisation of the form \(ax^2+bx+c\) and Factorisation by completing the Perfect Square.

This assignment focuses on Factorisation. The concepts covered are Division of Polynomials using Factorisation, Dividing two Polynomials using Long Division and Finding the Error in Algebraic Expressions.
This assignment focuses on Introduction to Graphs. The concept covered is Line Graphs and how to read the graph to obtain specific data.

This assignment focuses on Introduction to Graphs. The concepts covered are Linear Graphs, Location of points based on their co-ordinates and Application of linear graphs for dependent and independent variable.
The concepts covered in the following assignment are: Direct Proportions, Word Problems on Direct Proportions, Interpreting tabular data as Direct Proportions.
The concepts covered in the following assignment are: Inverse Proportions, Word Problems on Inverse Proportions, Interpreting tabular data as Inverse Proportions.
This assignment focuses on Squares and Square Roots. The concepts covered are Squares or Natural Numbers and Properties of Square Numbers.

This assignment focuses on Squares and Square Roots. The concepts covered are Squares or Natural Numbers without Actual Multiplication, Pythagorean Triplets and Finding Square Roots using Prime Factorisation.
This assignment focuses on Squares and Square Roots. The concepts covered are Square Roots of Natural Numbers and Finding Square Roots using Long Division Method.
The concepts covered in the following assignment are: Usual form of a number, Generalized form of a number, Representation of numbers, Letters for Digits.
The concepts covered in the following assignment are: Divisibility tests of 10, 5, 2, 9, 3 and 6.
This assignment focuses on Cubes and Cube Roots. The concepts covered are Cubes of Natural Numbers, Properties of Cube Numbers and Representation of Perfect Cubes as a product of their Prime Factors.
This assignment focuses on Cubes and Cube Roots. The concepts covered are Cube Roots of Cube Numbers, Finding Cube Roots through Prime Factorisation and Estimation of Cube Roots.
This assignment covers the concepts of Classification of Polygons, Diagonals of Polygons, Angle sum Property and the Sum of exterior angles of a polygon.
This assignment covers the concepts of Properties of Parallelograms.
This assignment covers the concepts of Types of Parallelograms.
This assignment covers the following topics: Ratios, Percentages, Word Problems on Percentage, Word Problems on Ratios, Ratio-Percentage Conversions.
This assignment covers the following topics: Increase and Decrease of Percentages, Estimation in Percentages, Profit and Loss, Discounts, Sales Tax, Value added Tax.
This assignment covers the following topics: Simple Interest, Compound Interest,Applications of Compound Interests, Word problems on Simple and Compound interest.
